	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is kind of a moot point now that there is a monk newbie quest in freeport, but if you need something until you can get there, there is a place nearby. Go in to the sewers of Qeynos under the bridge by the bank. In this section there are 3 froglocks in the water who are approx level 4, they drop netted armor, and very rarely mesh. The pieces you want most are gloves and sandals ( to kick and punch wisps) since they need a magic weapon to hit. There is also a quest for a newbie weapon in freeport that is 5 24 h2h and magic, though the mob for it is as much an undercon as Dorn, and more difficult than any for the other newbie weapons IMHO. For a non twink the newbie armor in freeport is great, and has lots of sta and agi, which I prefer as my main stats ( I prefer the defensive route ).<br><br>Denellron, 16th monk, Firiona Vie<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
