	   <tr><td colspan=2>It should be noted to all newbies that the value of wisps for anyone come with the rare drop of the greater light stone (GLS). Many people mistakenly just sell them for about 3pp to a vendor. The best thing to do is take them to the gypsies. I use the ones in NK, but I know that there is a similar quest in the oasis but I've never really done it.<br><br>Hail the female gypsies till you find one who tells you she is the keeper of the Concordance of Research. When you find her give her (don't sell) a GLS. She will give you a Concordance of Research which you can sell for 8pp. For the level of wisps (around 10-14) this is awesome loot. You might also want to keep the book as a light weight 6 slot giant container; at 0.4 stone it's somewhat better than a large bag or backpack. Just remember that if you get in trouble the guards do not kill wisps so you will need to zone.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Apr 18 14:03:15 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
