	   <tr><td colspan=2>At level 9, it's not a real problem for you...yet. Where I am now, I lose 8-10 ac if I pick up a few coins when I'm at the weight cap. Luckily, this cap goes up as you go along, but not much.<br><br>The penalty to ac you take is probably compensated by the heavier armor you wear for now.<br><br>Regarding your weapon, I'd say hang on to it. You need to keep your 1hb-skill up. Besides, your fists are damage 5, delay 36 at this point, so you are actually doing alright. Just be sure to train everything. Even get a cracked staff or something to make sure your 2hb is up to par as well.<br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=115679 target=_new><b>Niteklaw Ahzi'Dahaka</b></a><br>Brother of the Celestial Fists<br>Povar Tarew Alliance, Xev.</td></tr>
