	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, normally you can't. There are very, very few light 2-handed blunt weapons out there, and they are rarely available below level 50. If you DO train 2hb (and you should) you will be trading something off, so getting a good one becomes a bit more important.<br><br>At lvl 26, my suggestion is the Adamantite Bo Stick. You might need to get rid of it at lvl 30 when it procs, since it becomes much less manageble at this point, and can only be used in a few situation. But untill then, it has a good ratio, and at dam 19, delay 30, it is a blindingly fast 2-hander...which is what you are looking for to train.<br><br>Prices for these have rock-bottomed, and I would be surprised if you could pick one up for 250-300pp.<br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=115679 target=_new><b>Niteklaw Ahzi'Dahaka</b></a><br>Brother of the Celestial Fists<br>Povar Tarew Alliance, Xev.</td></tr>
