	   <tr><td colspan=2>With just 5k, you probably won't get any haste...But here is what you could do in the way of gear (May take a few nights in GFay)<br><br>Chest: Crystal Covered Shroud (250pp)<br>Legs: Gatorscale Leggings (350pp)<br>Arms: Azure Sleeves (400pp)<br>Ears: Cougar Claw (300pp per pair), Orc Fang (80-100pp per pair) or Electrum Black Saphire(500pp pr. pair)<br>Head: Froggy Crown (1000pp)<br>Shoulders: Drolvarg Mantle (100pp)<br>Hands: Gem Inlaid Gauntlets (150pp)<br>Back: Wu's if Human (75pp) Kunzar Cloak is Iksar (150pp)<br>Waist: Thick Leather Apron (20pp)<br>Feet: Wu's (60pp)<br>Wrists: Symbol of Loyalty to Vox if Human (200pp for a pair). Erollisi Bracer (150pp), Wu's (50pp) and/or Tar Goo Strands (400pp) if Iksar.<br>Fingers: Velium Fire Wedding Rings (1000pp for a pair).<br>Face: Sarnak Hide mask (500pp)<br>Neck: Orc Fang Necklace (200pp)<br>Weapons: FB&nbsp;&nbsp;(1hb, secondary)(300pp) and CoT (1hb Primary) (500pp), and Adamantite Bo Stick (350pp) (2hb)<br><br>All this puts you somewhere between 5kpp and 6kpp, depending on luck, availablity and your skills as a merchant. It's a fairly solid Gear-setup, I think, and it should keep you reasonably within your weight-limits.<br><br>Good Luck!<br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=115679 target=_new><b>Niteklaw Ahzi'Dahaka</b></a><br>Brother of the Celestial Fists<br>Povar Tarew Alliance, Xev.</td></tr>
