	   <tr><td colspan=2>For all those fellow monks out there trying to get Raster he still does pop!&nbsp;&nbsp;Got him Friday night.  For reference for all those getting ready to camp him I offer the following guidance:<br>1.  Depending on your gear you can probably break the mino camp and set up at about 44.  I did at 45 with no problem (923 AC, 1560 hp, using Gorgana Spiked club and KD, with silver Chiltin hand wraps).<br>2.  Follow the guide at monkly-business.com.  It works very well.<br>3.  In 3 RL days he popped at least 3 times.  I think this may be a slight increase, but still a very long camp.  Bring plenty of bandages, food and water.<br><br>Good luck all,<br><br>Uniero<br>46 Human Monk<br>Officer Odin's Ghost<br>7th Hammer<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
