	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well i don't think my answers are going to be much use, but i will try to answer the ones i can.<br><br>A1) I think UGUK is great, although fightin in there by yourself without PLing is tough, and gettin a group there at those levels might be hard. I am finding unfortunately that gettin a group is difficult anywhere except the most obvious places pre 30, cause everyone just wants to get out of these levels, not play throught them.<br><br>A2)Armor they drop is just like most dungeons the loot is on a table, and they have some percentage chance of dropping a piece or armor(Type depends on type and level of mob) I am not very familiar with them dropping jewels.. if they do i would say it is rare.<br><br>A3) Not Sure.<br><br>A4) Not Sure.<br><br>A5) It actually is sometimes possible to get a small group here, I wouldn't try to make the trip till at least 25.. <br><br>A6) I don't think the bane is important, except that it makes it creature specific.. like the wizard bane line of spells.<br><br>A7) Monk Weapon skills are (lvl+1)X5 and it is the same for H2H, I am only 45 though, and it may change when you get beyond that however I can confirm that is what it is up till 45.. other skills (Offense, defense, dual wield, double attack) don't all follow same formula.<br><br>A8)&nbsp;&nbsp;I am not sure why those two classes would make it easier to get gear than just starting a monk and gaining experience while doing it.. in fact a monk is better naked than any other class i know of.... As far as whether i think it is &quot;wrong&quot; to twink.. absolutely not.  It is a game and gettin levels and having fun is the goal, not some kind of test to see if you can strauggle through 600 deaths to make level 60 with no help.. in fact no help could mean no grouping.. and very few classes could make it to 60 without that kind of &quot;help.&quot;..  Do I think the game started out as being intended to be played by twinks??.. no... But Verant has consistently made this game harder and harder.. twinkin and PLing are almost necesary in my mind to get out of the boring and hard to group levels of 1-20..<br><br>I would also like to take this time to say I think it sucks Verant does nerf the game.. Fear kitin by necs is a good example of where verant forces a class to play a certain way through nerfs.. because necs can kick ass with fear kiting they have been nerfed so much that they can't kill anything any other way... (gettin off soap box now)<br><br>Hope this helps a little.. good luck when you do start your monk.<br><br>-Pulrial Phazt<br>45 Monk, Brell<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
