	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.72]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The use of FD has been covered very well, and I have used ID to fear kite also.&nbsp;&nbsp;However I have also used it (in outdoor situations) to either break up 2 MOBS I was facing without having to FD split them (typically because there was an add during the fight), and sometimes to get me a break to bandage.  If chasing the MOB would put me into more harms way (which happens), but he won't bring friends back with him I use the time to get 2 bandages in (100 hp in my case).  This worked great for the orcs in CC.  There are all kinds of ways to use these skills to your advantage. Try them out, and if they don't work we can always FD lol<br><br><br>Uniero<br>45 Human Monk<br>Officer Odin's Ghost<br>7th Hammer<br>(Raster, Raster here boy.....64 PH and counting)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
